@rck-innovium @abdosi Can we get a closure on this please ?  As @phshaikh said, I dont think its useful to identify only a subset of mirrors to be sampled and let the remaining mirrors unsampled.

In order to sample only certain mirror sessions, it can be achieved by specifying the sampling rate (SAI_MIRROR_SESSION_ATTR_SAMPLE_RATE) on the mirror object itself. The main motivation of this is to share the mirror sessions across different ports but use different sampling rates.

